  "date": "2026-03-18 08:49:00",
  "author": "十字路口Crossing",
  "siteName": "十字路口Crossing",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>Jack</span> <span>2026-03-18 16:49</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f6fee211&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fa16Y4PLxPqkvLWgiay456T6LpzBoZz8MrHEibkzmqicvdYia26ibwFru8AnW9aPs021yG017czeZd4aaOUeM2z22k7P0HlZsuREbvAqiaqnpXCXpY%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63,63,63);line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"line-height: 26px;word-spacing: normal;hyphens: auto;text-align: left;outline: 0;max-width: 100%;border-top: none;border-right: none;border-bottom: none;display: block;overflow: auto;padding: 10px;margin: 20px 0;border-left: 8px solid #222222;background-color: #f5f5f5;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">当 AI 学会「不直接给答案」</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622848\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e4cfacde&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqlKsKpgsy0rI85UQKqD69gUZJRQxeVWxmwic2DXmicy7DcUB8Q9U62eibqicspeUb8NHVCTEIVAgCGokiau0qTdPnO1mU9xUvJ3xOAU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: right;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 0px;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">👦🏻 作者: Jack</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: right;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 0px;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🥷 编辑: Koji</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: right;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 0px;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🧑‍🎨 排版: NCon</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.12129629629629629\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622836\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6951d8bc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqkhliaeYNCf0xLK99riahNiaV3icbmX2ck3WhZKSkUJhAF0XFXT1opy2FicUTgOjuqLp7ED7Pt4lC68kCcXgfvlibqgg0pBLdh7P3LWU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">今年 1 月，马斯克在 Peter Diamandis 主持的播客 Moonshots&nbsp;<a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mmvo06og-otgaun\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#220</a>&nbsp;里聊了 173 分钟。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其中有一个观点很刺耳：未来上大学的唯一理由，可能就是社交——置身于同龄人之中，在一个可以交流、竞争、互相影响的物理环境里。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">至于知识本身，马斯克说：</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">“交给 AI 吧，它绝对会比人类老师做得更好！”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原因很简单但是很残酷：一个人类老师站在讲台上面对着几十个资质各异的学生，跑得快的孩子觉得无聊透顶，跑得慢的孩子听得像天书，而没听懂的孩子，往往连举手提问的勇气都没有。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但 AI 不一样。它永远不会不耐烦，也永远不会觉得你笨，你哪里不懂就问哪里。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"display: block;line-height: 1.5;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size: 17px;font-weight: bold;margin: 40px 0;width: fit-content;color: #222222;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">🚥</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近，十字路口内容团队，测试了豆包App里「豆包爱学」这个功能。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">深度体验几天后，我们有一个比较直观的感受：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 除了「直接给答案」，也开始学着像一个真正的老师那样「手把手教你」了。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.46296296296296297\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622838\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b3b41f8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqlgnyttqBJ367WBiaj02UCwvVPsicEfiaQSIolyvtNdrNnm0Zzics8NicwRMhib6ADpcXDxFrZpbKM6nDQvqarbxNPic0M61t3vKoJctY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"display: block;line-height: 1.5;font-size: 24px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-weight: bold;margin: 80px auto 40px auto;width: fit-content;color: #407600;text-align: center;padding: 0 1em;border-bottom: 8px solid #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">从拍照搜题到拍照讲题</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去的很多年，搜题 App 一直是渗透率最高的教育工具。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">遇到不会的题，拿手机一拍，几秒钟内解题步骤和标准答案就可以立即出现在屏幕上。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但「豆包爱学」拿到同一道题之后，做的事情完全不一样。我们用「豆包爱学」拍下这道初中数学的几何题：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1588235294117647\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"680\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622837\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ca5eb2d8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmpgMBSLmgF2OicrXZL6sD0LicEArKsVMDq87K66xiaLOmm9NltqLEuIDcyxVXGBt7dS7cQN5SPkiaiah8iaen5v5Pp9TYjiaBoiaqh4Fc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来，他开始理解问题、定位相关知识点 、梳理讲解逻辑</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8555555555555555\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622847\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a50ac7c2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqlo1YzqW9iacFklZcRicsdiaichW0NjICBSb8kZ8OicFGfEZZicdKHcxRCcAvLm6iaS7TicjfmEtv8RFQHunoIIDjP7lub7kv8FvtYpgcY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以看到不是直接给到答案，而是像个真人老师一样，一步一步，引导你等着你提问，根据你的的反馈来调整教学的节奏和内容</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个过程中甚至会主动问：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);font-weight: bold;\">“这个公式你还记得吗？”、“这一步的简便计算你看明白了吗？”</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.837037037037037\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622840\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7bba2fda&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqnpKmmmtNnEY6jsEoyjWmsIUInQMiaRhmGtbQAqcMpicgFIv2ETPosmGq0JX5Xnv9v120EOcLoTuLfBsbpfkIJjHCicicB6lcosrRw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">那如果我听完第一轮讲解确实还是没听懂，怎么办呢？你可以直接在对话框说话，随时打断，它会根据你的问题重新引导你，再次讲解！这是人类老师不一定具有的耐心。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.837037037037037\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622839\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e317a2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqlEAKlrWlyiaOicxIVfzGVeh61Gy1khmaJH9yppY4hjr3Gkd7QzfmnjdumyjLAa18eZozBhRA1WcanaWibGtkuj8SUSKhxBtOyK4k%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统搜题 App 的逻辑是：</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">你不会，我告诉你答案，</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">「豆包爱学」的逻辑是：</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">你不会，我引导你思考，帮你想明白</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这两个字的区别：「告诉」和「思考」，可能就是 AI 教育从工具变成老师的分水岭。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"display: block;line-height: 1.5;font-size: 24px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-weight: bold;margin: 80px auto 40px auto;width: fit-content;color: #407600;text-align: center;padding: 0 1em;border-bottom: 8px solid #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 老师讲到哪，黑板就跟到哪</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">光靠语音讲，其实还不够。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多学科的难点之所以难，就是因为它是抽象的，你听懂了每个字，但脑子里就是拼不出那个画面。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这也是传统线上教育一直没解决好的问题：老师在讲，学生在听，但中间缺一块黑板。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「豆包爱学」补上了这块「黑板」。在讲解过程中，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);font-weight: bold;\">它会</span></span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">实时生成可视化的板书</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们拿「急刹车时身体为什么会前倾？」这道物理趣味题试了一下：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 15px;padding: 10px;color: #333;background-color: #fafafa;border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,.3) 0px 2px 10px;overflow-x: auto;text-align: left;font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"></p>\n   <pre style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;overflow-x: auto;background: transparent;\"><code style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.65;word-break: normal;display: block;color: #333;\"><span leaf=\"\">急刹车时，身体为什么会前倾？</span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先，它精准定位到了这道题背后的物理学经典概念：「惯性」。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但它没有上来就甩定义，而是先还原急刹车的完整过程：刹车前、刹车时、身体前倾，让你先「看到」现象，再理解原理。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">甚至还顺手纠正了日常生活中对这个现象最常见的理解误区。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整个板书是跟着 AI 老师的语音讲解实时生成的，讲到哪一步，图就跟到哪一步。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5509259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622845\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=47f668ab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmU9Xh7voad7ehYicylPfAekzVk5lLVhFfGbwdc7g6rBURnQZmdhjc3RfBJGICg1TAgra79v3YFzfhVsnNlLlEjVnjecQKHW5Qc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比起单纯听一段语音，这种「边听边看」的节奏确实更容易跟住，整个过程可以通过下面这个录屏感受一下</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.172222222222222\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622846\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ef86619e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmh6cM9ZwT4Is8B5Bn11ze9iav4pbLPANwHroZSzALibiaupl79bphhlIDKfeDZfW1ribLcm0marM6OQ2ERYEVKbPpKFSt6o3FpEok%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">再看这道几何题的板书，辅助线怎么画、面积怎么拆、等量替换怎么做，全部一步步用图拆开：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 15px;padding: 10px;color: #333;background-color: #fafafa;border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,.3) 0px 2px 10px;overflow-x: auto;text-align: left;font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"></p>\n   <pre style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;overflow-x: auto;background: transparent;\"><code style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.65;word-break: normal;display: block;color: #333;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个直角三角形，两条直角边分别是 6 cm 和 8 cm，求斜边上的高</span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.172222222222222\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622850\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=89e40341&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqnEx2iaC111jZ109oWBllevgqC3nqA7IgQbpKJ1ibwN3ZicDjHg6G9Nq41mvEC6Ft9sLtTfhDUWlXz4yypNOL97tz9dYQ6vQ6I1tI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">讲完还没完。每一轮讲解结束后，它会主动抛出一个延伸问题：「你知道什么是内切圆吗？在这个直角三角形中，内切圆半径是多少？」</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它不让你停在「会做这道题」，而是推你往「会做这类题」走一步</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0078328981723237\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"766\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622841\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=effcd95e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqnK8xdQ9SficZKzKHZSZyDXxP1EFGPoUmiaqWsJk602FJwE6oErfKHic7Om4ahCMibLPr4yTKCLZ5lvo7MD44sib3JibtibuibsMbzuibCc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">语音讲解这块也值得说一下。语速可以自己调，听不清就放慢，觉得啰嗦就倍速。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.725925925925926\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622842\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=47df03ae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqm6g2FjXyJOP89sshhw117wGW8iaXTXNlibt6rQeIXY26BsU1T6Va1aOzMOqiagicEO75YDpbJD7k9k6zUiaLzzUSCGT1tvxbAX0O7U%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">更有意思的是，它支持方言讲解，我们试了一下用东北话讲物理的惯性定律，效果相当上头。粤语和英语也都支持，对于英语学科或者习惯母语思维的用户来说，这个细节其实挺实用的。</span></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这块「智能板书」体验下来，感觉就是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);font-weight: bold;\">把课堂里最好的那块黑板塞进了手机</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">回想一下，传统课堂里最大的遗憾是什么？不是老师讲得不好，而是一个老师只有一块黑板、一种节奏，却要面对几十个完全不同的大脑。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「豆包爱学」做的事情，本质上就是给每个人配了一块只属于自己的黑板，和一个永远愿意再讲一遍的老师。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"display: block;line-height: 1.5;font-size: 24px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-weight: bold;margin: 80px auto 40px auto;width: fit-content;color: #407600;text-align: center;padding: 0 1em;border-bottom: 8px solid #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">不止答题，还能聊「百科」</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你以为「豆包爱学」只能拍题讲题，那确实还是低估了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它真正让我们觉得有意思的地方在于：你可以拿任何一个「为什么」去问它，不限于课本，不限于学科。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如我们试了一个小朋友在饭桌上很可能会问、但大人很难讲清楚的问题：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 15px;padding: 10px;color: #333;background-color: #fafafa;border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,.3) 0px 2px 10px;overflow-x: auto;text-align: left;font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"></p>\n   <pre style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;overflow-x: auto;background: transparent;\"><code style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.65;word-break: normal;display: block;color: #333;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么飞机那么重却能飞起来？</span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.172222222222222\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501622851\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fe463412&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqlEKMglIsrUOic000O76lDZmEFKibJaoD9lvsiaiacp54MUU0Wx7quFtDh3vYpuZeM3J1WB9suOuYJuP556uZW7ibNurtEF892njKZc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63,63,63);line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它没有甩出一段「伯努利原理」的定义，而是从「你用嘴吹一张纸会发生什么」这个生活场景开始介绍，一步步搭建到机翼的截面形状、气流速度差、升力的产生。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整个讲解有画面、有节奏，一个没学过物理的小学生也能看懂。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们又试了一个更天马行空的：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;margin: 20px 10px;display: block;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 15px;padding: 10px;color: #333;background-color: #fafafa;border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,.3) 0px 2px 10px;overflow-x: auto;text-align: left;font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"></p>\n   <pre style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;overflow-x: auto;background: transparent;\"><code style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.65;word-break: normal;display: block;color: #333;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果地球突然停止自转，会发生什么？</span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.172222222222222\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501622852\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0b4fe432&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqkyicFyoPe9LIrsL2YbSUu5nMnDvdGlGq2TCU8vicjVD9CDYSvTibqkfMqP8Jbg5eCYDicxhDVsZYbsfgd77OObl0uzDGE7otWclpc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63,63,63);line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种问题没有标准答案，但「豆包爱学」的处理方式很聪明：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以看到，它依然会拆结构、配板书、给延伸，和前面讲数学题是同一套逻辑。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个能力把「豆包爱学」的使用场景拉得很宽：它更像是一个随时可以陪你聊「为什么」的百科老师。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">小到「为什么蚊子专门咬我不咬别人」，大到「宇宙的尽头是什么」，它都能接得住。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🚥 &nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">另外值得一提的是，「豆包爱学」还有一个独立 App，在 AI 老师的核心能力之外，补齐了作业批改、AI 错题本、作文辅导这些日常学习场景。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7175925925925926\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622843\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=79859428&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fa16Y4PLxPqnke2VT7pZ2lIoLU3VibibL5H3ksDvcA7WN99bGzvUPo7wVKRMwhZWoPeQn8XLjsPfcefksicdOYDWtFJcLImkwDTgxrWaYLcDu4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 教育这件事聊了好多年，大部分产品最后都变成了更快的搜索引擎。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「豆包爱学」让我们看到了一个不太一样的方向：它不急着给你答案，它想先确认你真的听懂了，并且陪伴你，直到你真的听懂了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">回到开头马斯克那个判断：AI 会比人类老师做得更好。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">或许这话现在说可能还早了点，但至少有一件事，AI 确实已经做到了大多数人类老师很难做到的：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">对每一个学生，都保持同样的耐心，不管你问第几遍。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;margin: 0;padding-bottom: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63,63,63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">光是这一点，就已经值得认真期待了！</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622849\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ed81d7b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqkuAg3uBGzX4Uibsz6gNW65RLeUVVgQHTjWjmknUEoffNLKuHdF9SOYT7iaCcaqB4EibQylZyXucODYQia7cKpicEBXjGOhxb2X5Anc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622844\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a6aa0c82&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqlxtzCmTUpiaMDj1XwxORS8g7vOa8ThB8qM3xrwOEicEGHWDToMOibDAnIRIqkfhdg21c1FGGq4NPzurhiapBs4zGPrB6qMUFT07ibc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"%27%27\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=4883dcc9&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzAxMDMxOTI2NA%3D%3D%26mid%3D2649106501%26idx%3D1%26sn%3Df58a9785d31a85edb9b7219e00d2c79e\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深度评测了字节跳动旗下「豆包爱学」功能，展示了 AI 教育从单纯“搜题给答案”向“启发式引导”与“实时可视化板书”进化的新范式。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深度评测了字节跳动旗下「豆包爱学」功能，展示了 AI 教育从单纯“搜题给答案”向“启发式引导”与“实时可视化板书”进化的新范式。",
  "summary": "文章通过对「豆包爱学」功能的深度实测，探讨了 AI 在教育领域的角色转变。作者指出，不同于传统搜题 App 直接给出标准答案的逻辑，豆包爱学采用了“启发式教学”模式，通过互动提问、实时生成可视化板书以及支持多方言的语音讲解，模拟真人老师的教学过程。其核心亮点在于能够根据学生的反馈调整节奏，将抽象的物理或几何概念通过动态板书直观呈现，并能处理跨学科的百科类问题。文章认为，这种从“告诉”到“引导思考”的转变，以及 AI 具备的无限耐心，标志着 AI 正在从辅助工具进化为真正的个性化老师。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 教育正从“结果导向”的搜题工具转向“过程导向”的启发式教学。",
      "explanation": "传统工具侧重直接提供答案，而新型 AI 老师通过分步引导、主动提问和逻辑梳理，旨在帮助学生理解解题背后的原理，而非仅仅完成作业。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“实时可视化板书”解决了线上教育中抽象概念难以传达的痛点。",
      "explanation": "通过语音与动态绘图的同步，AI 能将复杂的物理现象或几何辅助线绘制过程直观化，实现了“边听边看”的沉浸式学习体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 的核心竞争力在于其“无限耐心”带来的教育公平与个性化。",
      "explanation": "AI 不受情绪影响，能够针对不同资质的学生提供千人千面的讲解节奏，解决了传统课堂中老师难以兼顾所有学生进度的结构性矛盾。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "这两个字的区别：‘告诉’和‘思考’，可能就是 AI 教育从工具变成老师的分水岭。",
    "AI 老师讲到哪，黑板就跟到哪。",
    "它不急着给你答案，它想先确认你真的听懂了，并且陪伴你，直到你真的听懂了。",
    "AI 确实已经做到了大多数人类老师很难做到的：对每一个学生，都保持同样的耐心，不管你问第几遍。"
  ],
